Class CalculationValidationException

  java.lang.Throwable

                      xbrlcore.exception.CalculationValidationException
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class CalculationValidationException
extends InstanceValidationException

This class represents an Exception which is thrown if a calculation rule according to the calculation linkbase does not validate.

Besides a describing text, this class contains detailed information about the reason for the violated calculation rule.

Author:
Daniel Hamm
